titles.title: Increasing the statutory limit on the public debt.

action.text: Pursuant to the provisions of H. Con. Res. 64, H.J. Res. 174 is considered passed House.

The Chair announced that, pursuant to rule XLIX, as a result of the adoption of H. Con. Res. 64 by the House and Senate, H.J. Res. 174 was engrossed and deemed to have passed the House on March 31, 1993.
Received in the Senate. Read the first time. Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under Read the First Time.

calendar.text: Read the second time. Placed on Senate Legislative Calendar under General Orders. Calendar No. 58.

bill.summary: 4/1/1993--Introduced. Increases the statutory limit on the public debt.
